Wow, there are two rooms numbered 1467 in the Council base?

::Killfest::

Killfest raises an eyebrow plate, entering the middle room, his team 
taking the others. Over a thousand rooms? How many bots did this team 
have?"

Scyther enters one of the rooms numbered 1467, Demise entering the 
other one (numbered 1467). EndBringer takes 1469 and Greven 1470.
